<dl id="n18115g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n18" href="#n18115g">N18 (VI.B.8)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n18all.htm#n18115g"> 115(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> road hog </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: IT 250716-6/8: <b>RISKS OF THE ROAD</b> &hellip; I have nothing but praise for the Civic Guards, who are courtesy itself when appealed to; but they are too courteous to &ldquo;<mark>road hogs,</mark>&rdquo; who are without regard for the comfort and pleasure of others. One constantly sees offences committed &hellip;. </mm> </dd></dl>
